stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> REQUESTED
  REQUESTED --> MATCHING: dispatch
  MATCHING --> DRIVER_ASSIGNED: accept
  MATCHING --> REQUESTED: timeout retry
  DRIVER_ASSIGNED --> EN_ROUTE_PICKUP: driver started
  EN_ROUTE_PICKUP --> ARRIVED_PICKUP: at pickup
  ARRIVED_PICKUP --> ON_TRIP: passenger onboard
  ON_TRIP --> COMPLETED: drop off
  COMPLETED --> [*]
  REQUESTED --> CANCELLED: customer cancel
  MATCHING --> CANCELLED: give up
  DRIVER_ASSIGNED --> CANCELLED: either party
  ON_TRIP --> CANCELLED: exception
  CANCELLED --> [*]
